data.description: Located in Panama City Beach near Front Beach Road, shopping and restaurants. Each residence enjoys subtle hints of southern charm and peacefulness. This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath has a waterfront view of the lake/pond with no neighbors directly behind you. Walking into the foyer, you are greeted by a spacious open floor plan with 9 foot ceilings, large upgraded kitchen with granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances and breakfast bar overlooking the family/living room. For convenience, you have a 1/2 bath on the first floor. The second floor incorporates a large master bedroom with Jacuzzi/shower, and walk in closets.
